    • Uses of PathStrategy in fr.ecp.IS1220.myVelib.core

      Classes in fr.ecp.IS1220.myVelib.core that implement PathStrategy 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AvoidPlus
      A path strategy for finding the path between two localizations which requires to walk the minimal distance and doesn't make the ride end in a Plus station.
      class  FastestPath
      A path strategy for finding the path between two localizations which takes the minimal time.
      class  MinimalWalking
      A path strategy for finding the path between two localizations which requires to walk the minimal distance.
      class  PreferPlus
      A path strategy for finding the path between two localizations which makes the ride end in a Plus station provided it keeps the walk distance close to the minimal.
      class  PreserveDistribution
      A path strategy for finding the path between two localizations which is a compromise between the walk distance and the conservation of a uniform distribution of bicycles among the stations of the network.
